Author: Ashley Fletcher
Title: Listen to Elizabeth Potthast cover an iconic Patsy Cline song
Text:
Elizabeth Potthast is ready to get her singing career started. Pic credit: TLC
90 Day Fiance star Elizabeth Potthast continues to share her singing skills with fans of the show.
After a clip of her singing a lullaby to her daughter surfaced online, viewers of the show have been sharing their thoughts on Elizabeth's vocal abilities.
During the season premiere of Happily Ever After?, Elizabeth revealed that she is taking steps to jumpstart her singing career.
As she and her husband build their dream home, they are dedicating a room to become her studio so that she can rehearse and record her own music.

Author: Em Short
Title: Becoming Elizabeth: Historical Figures vs. TV Characters
Text: The new Starz series Becoming Elizabeth follows the young Elizabeth Tudor after the death of her father, the notorious King Henry VIII of England. The historical drama, created by Anya Reiss, depicts the then-future queen of England as she navigates the treacherous waters of the English court. Like many period pieces, Becoming Elizabeth has its dramatized historical inaccuracies, but the show must be praised for its mostly true-to-life depictions of the most important characters of the English Court.

Title: Queen Elizabeth II not attending Scotland's Highland Games amid ‘mobility issues'
Text:
2:51 Reflecting on the impact of Queen Elizabeth II as she marks 70 years on the throne There is no denying that Queen Elizabeth has been an enduring presence in the world. Dawna Friesen reflects on her seven decades on the throne – Jun 5, 2022 
 Queen Elizabeth II will skip the Braemar Gathering, a popular Highland Games event, as she struggles with issues getting around.
The 96-year-old monarch previously decided to formally appoint Britain's new prime minister on Tuesday at Balmoral Castle in Scotland, where she is vacationing, rather than return to London for the traditional ceremony at Buckingham Palace.

Author: Febriyantino Nur Pratama
Title: Di Mata Ikang Fawzi Soal Kepemimpinan Monarki Ratu Elizabeth II
Text: Jakarta - Meninggalnya Ratu Elizabeth II membuat dunia berduka. Lantas melihat ke belakang, Ikang Fawzi turut mengomentari gaya kepemimpinan mendiang Ratu Elizabeth."Monarki ya, di dalam hati gue yang terdalam gue nggak suka monarki. Maksudnya kita sudah lama meninggalkan monarki. Tapi di Inggris, monarki yang memang rakyatnya sudah siap dan kekuasaannya dibatasi iya, kan, ceremonial," kata Ikang Fawzi di Cawang, Jakarta Timur, Jumat (9/9/2022).Ikang juga akui tak suka dengan kepemimpinan Ratu Elizabeth II yang bergaya monarki.

Text: Expect delays, especially during busy travel times: The Ministry of Transportation has scheduled seven closures in Niagara on Sept. 2 for roadwork on Queen Elizabeth Way. Title: Peel highway closures for planned roadwork (Sept. 2)
Text: Avoid traffic jams before they happen: The Ministry of Transportation has scheduled 39 closures in Peel on Sept. 2 for roadwork on Highway 401, Highway 403, Highway 410, Highway 427 and Queen Elizabeth Way. Highway 401 eastbound at Winston Churchill Boulevard: two right lanes closed until Sept. 2 at 5 a.m. Highway 401 eastbound between 407 and Ninth Line Road: two left lanes closed until Sept. 2 at 5 a.m. Highway 401 eastbound between Derry Road and Highway 403: two left lanes closed until Sept. 2 at 5 a.

Author: WITN Web Team
Title: Elizabeth City police searching for man wanted for murder
Text: ELIZABETH CITY, N.C. (WITN) - Elizabeth City police have announced warrants for a man wanted for a murder last week.Police said that warrants for first degree murder and assault with a deadly weapon with intent to kill inflicting serious injury were obtained this past Monday for James Felton, Jr., 38, of Elizabeth City. Investigators believe Felton is responsible for killing Marcus Moore, 29, of Elizabeth City, back on August 27th. Moore was found dead in the on the 500 block of White Street. Felton should be considered armed and dangerous.

Author: Wahyu Setyo Widodo
Title: Ratu Elizabeth II yang Selalu Bawa Stok Darah dan Baju Hitam Saat Traveling
Text: London - Ratu Elizabeth II telah berpulang di umur 96 tahun. Selama menjabat sebagai Ratu Inggris, ternyata dia selalu berpergian keliling dunia membawa stok darah dan baju hitam. Buat apa?Ratu Elizabeth II dikenal sebagai kepala negara yang paling banyak persiapan sebelum bepergian melakukan kunjungan ke beberapa negara. Salah satu barang yang tidak boleh lupa dibawa oleh sang ratu adalah stok darah.Ya, ketika melakukan kunjungan ke berbagai negara, Ratu Elizabeth II selalu membawa persediaan darah dalam kantong-kantong yang siap untuk ditransfusikan.

Title: Những thứ đáng ngạc nhiên thuộc sở hữu của Nữ hoàng Anh Elizabeth II
Text:
Nhảy đến nội dung
 
Nữ hoàng Anh Elizabeth II sở hữu tất cả cá heo, cá tầm và cá voi ở Vương quốc Anh. Điều này bắt nguồn từ một đạo luật được ban hành dưới thời Vua Edward II vào năm 1324 và vẫn còn được duy trì cho tới ngày nay. 
Nữ hoàng Elizabeth II sở hữu 6 kỷ lục Guinness thế giới, đó là Nữ hoàng Anh lớn tuổi nhất, Quốc vương sống thọ nhất thế giới, Nữ hoàng trị vì lâu nhất thế giới, người trị vị một triều đại lâu nhất, kỷ lục được in chân dung lên nhiều loại tiền tệ nhất và nữ hoàng sở hữu khối tài sản lớn nhất thế giới.

Nữ hoàng Elizabeth II sở hữu 6 kỷ lục Guinness thế giới , đó là Nữ hoàng Anh lớn tuổi nhất , Quốc vương sống thọ nhất thế giới , Nữ hoàng trị vì lâu nhất thế giới , người trị vị một triều đại lâu nhất , kỷ lục được chân dung lên nhiều loại tiền tệ nhất và nữ hoàng sở hữu khối tài sản lớn nhất thế giới .

Author: Derwesten
Title: Queen Elizabeth II: Weil das Unausweichliche näher rückt – Briten bereiten sich schon vor
Text: Früher oder später wird der Tag kommen, an dem aus England die Nachricht in die Welt gesendet wird, dass Queen Elizabeth ll. gestorben ist. Für diesen Fall will man im Buckingham Palace nicht unvorbereitet sein. Wenn Queen Elizabeth ll. stirbt, gibt es nämlich ganz bestimmte und strikte Ablaufpläne. Der Plan ist unter den Royals auch als Operation 'London Bridge' bekannt. Jetzt gibt es neue Details. Queen Elizabeth ll: Kirchen müssen Glockenklang ändern Wenn der Tag kommt, an dem die Königin stirbt, werden im ganzen Land die Kirchenglocken läuten.

Author: Stephanie Nolasco
Title: Queen Elizabeth, 96, to skip rarely missed Highland Games event amid mobility concerns
Text:
Queen Elizabeth will skip the Braemar Gathering, a popular Highland Games event and a much-loved outing, due to ongoing mobility concerns.

Her eldest son and heir, Prince Charles, who normally accompanies the monarch to the gathering, will attend. The decision was made for "the comfort" of the monarch, who has been struggling with issues getting around since last year.

The palace recently announced that Elizabeth will formally appoint Britain's new prime minister on Tuesday at Balmoral Castle in Scotland, not Buckingham Palace in London.
Title_without_stopwords: Queen Elizabeth , 96 , skip rarely missed Highland Games event amid mobility concerns
Text_without_stopwords: Queen Elizabeth skip Braemar Gathering , popular Highland Games event much-loved outing , due ongoing mobility concerns . Her eldest son heir , Prince Charles , normally accompanies monarch gathering , attend . The decision made `` comfort '' monarch , struggling issues getting around since last year . The palace recently announced Elizabeth formally appoint Britain 's new prime minister Tuesday Balmoral Castle Scotland , Buckingham Palace London .

Title: Queen Elizabeth, and the Power and Limitations of Inspiring Women
Text: There is a certain story about women’s progress that goes something like this: For too long, women have been held back by the personal prejudices of misguided individuals, and by society’s failure to imagine their potential for dazzling achievement.
